 Moshe Simons 
 
 
 
 Thanks for a great article! 
 Just to point our that the prices may change based on your location in the world – I checked the cost of tranexamic acid here in Israel – it costs about 1 shekel (25 cents) for a 500 mg pill and 5 shekels ($1.25) for a 500 mg ampule.  A huge difference in cost! 
 
 
