 Bill Fraser 
 
 
 
 I used the IV formulation for a stubborn anterior epistaxis a few months ago and had great success! Obviously the cost is significant. I wonder if a more dilute solution of the oral form applied to a pledget would be acceptable for epistaxis. I will have to give it a try. 
 
 
